ZH: 会长是这个组织的领导人。
EN: The president is the leader of this organization.

ZH: 请问，会长在哪儿？
EN: Excuse me, where is the president?

ZH: 会长今天有重要的会议。
EN: The president has an important meeting today.

ZH: 请问，你是新选的会长吗？
EN: Excuse me, are you the newly elected president?

ZH: 会长对组织起着至关重要的作用。
EN: The president plays a crucial role in the organization.

ZH: 这个组织的会长是一个很有能力的人。
EN: The president of this organization is a very capable person.

ZH: 请问，会长什么时候可以见我们？
EN: Excuse me, when can we see the president?

ZH: 会长已经在这个组织工作多年了。
EN: The president has been working in this organization for many years.

ZH: 会长提出了一个改革的建议。
EN: The president proposed a reform suggestion.

ZH: 请与会长预约一个见面时间。
EN: Please make an appointment with the president for a meeting.

ZH: 会长经常和会员们交流意见。
EN: The president often exchanges opinions with members.

ZH: 会长代表组织出席了国际会议。
EN: The president represented the organization at an international conference.

ZH: 新的会长将在下周正式就职。
EN: The new president will officially take office next week.

ZH: 请问，会长有没有空参加这个活动？
EN: Excuse me, does the president have time to attend this event?

ZH: 会长对组织的未来有很好的规划。
EN: The president has a good plan for the future of the organization.

ZH: 请向会长汇报最新的进展情况。
EN: Please report the latest progress to the president.

ZH: 会长正在和其他部门协商合作事宜。
EN: The president is negotiating cooperation with other departments.

ZH: 她是我们学校新的学生会长。
EN: She is the new student council president of our school.

ZH: 会长在公开演讲中表达了对员工的感谢之情。
EN: The president expressed gratitude to the employees in a public speech.

ZH: 会长很关心组织的发展方向。
EN: The president cares a lot about the development direction of the organization.
